OL,3,CITV Meridian bids farewell to Phil
OL,4,CHornby after 40 years
OL,6,FWATCH: A look back at ITV Meridian's
OL,7,FPhil Hornby throughout his career with
OL,8,Fthe company
OL,10,FITV Meridian's Political
OL,11,FCorrespondent, Phil Hornby retires
OL,12,Ftoday after a staggering 40 years at
OL,13,FITV.
OL,15,FHe's only just completed his final
OL,16,Felection coverage, which saw him once
OL,17,Fagain, reporting live from outside of
OL,18,F10 Downing Street.
