OL,3,CITV Meridian bids farewell to Phil
OL,4,CHornby after 40 years
OL,6,FThere was a brief exile to the BBC in
OL,7,Fthe Midlands, but he returned to ITV
OL,8,Fand Meridian in particular, where he
OL,9,Fbecame one of the best-known regional
OL,10,Fbroadcasters.
OL,12,FPhil's retirement is well-earned, but
OL,13,Fhis departure will leave a big gap
OL,14,Famong those colleagues who valued his
OL,15,Fjournalism and companionship so much.
OL,17,FWATCH: Phil signed off his final
OL,18,Fepisode of ITV Meridian's local
OL,19,Fpolitical programme The Last Word
