OL,3,CITV Meridian bids farewell to Phil
OL,4,CHornby after 40 years
OL,6,FRemembering his time at ITV, Phil
OL,7,Fsaid: "I began when we still filmed on
OL,8,Ffilm - working with editors who used
OL,9,Frazor blades and sellotape.
OL,11,F"A live involved a vehicle the size of
OL,12,Fa removal van which had to be booked
OL,13,Fweeks in advance.
OL,15,F"It's incredible how much has changed."
OL,17,FGood Morning Britain's Charlotte
OL,18,FHawkins worked with Phil Hornby
OL,19,Fpresenting Meridian Tonight.
