OL,3,CITV Meridian bids farewell to Phil
OL,4,CHornby after 40 years
OL,6,FRemembering their time together, she
OL,7,Fsaid: "I have so many special memories
OL,8,Fof our years working together
OL,9,Fpresenting Meridian Tonight.
OL,11,F"You were a joy to work with, such a
OL,12,Fprofessional, a master of interviewing
OL,13,F- but most of all - a good friend.
OL,15,F"We had so many adventures. I'm
OL,16,Fthinking of those outside broadcasts -
OL,17,Ffrom going up in a helicopter, to
OL,18,Fappearing in panto together - and who
OL,19,Fcould forget those summer roadshows,
OL,20,Fhanding out much sought after Meridian
OL,21,FTonight merchandise...
